// Pending/Warning
"bg-amber-500/15 text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400 border-amber-500/30 font-medium"

// Error/Danger
"bg-red-500/15 text-red-600 dark:text-red-400 border-red-500/30 font-medium"
```

### Text Hierarchy
```tsx
